# GitHub Pages — detail

- Site builds from **`gh-pages`**. **`git push` to `main`** does not refresh https://felex1896.github.io/field-ui-test/ without **`npm run deploy:gh-pages`** from **`field-demo/`** (uses **`base-href` `/field-ui-test/`**).
- Run deploy when playground-visible work is ready (typically after pushing to `main`).
- **Agent:** run deploy when appropriate, or say explicitly that the user should. Never assume push updated the live site.
